00:10:46,746 --> 00:10:48,360
s'iz geven a groys hoyz.

228
00:10:49,648 --> 00:10:53,557
tsu di muter's a shvester. UNK hot geheysn VASERMAN.

229
00:10:53,766 --> 00:10:55,245
Fishl VASERMAN.

230
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:58,890
az vifl mentshn hobn gevoynt in dem hoyz?

231
00:10:59,757 --> 00:11:01,658
