232
00:11:01,782 --> 00:11:03,986
di dray FLOOR ⟨hobn⟩ gekent

233
00:11:05,983 --> 00:11:06,824
bay

234
00:11:06,824 --> 00:11:09,403
z- ir veyst in di heym iz geven eyn shtub

235
00:11:09,578 --> 00:11:11,473
hobn mir gevoynt finef zeks mentshn.

236
00:11:11,473 --> 00:11:13,605
s'iz nisht gevezn azoy vi

237
00:11:13,425 --> 00:11:17,604
az ir zayt geven oyf eyn shtok? ayer mishpokhe, es iz geven es, oyf eyn shtok?

238
00:11:17,323 --> 00:11:23,105
yo. mir zenen gevezn oyf dem tsveytn. UNK dos heyst UNK oyf di FLOOR, un nakher ⟨dem⟩ ershtn shtok.

239
00:11:23,652 --> 00:11:24,894
un ver

240
00:11:23,837 --> 00:11:27,256
ober dos iz geven in tsveytn hoyz, nisht vu di BAKERY iz.

241
00:11:27,702 --> 00:11:29,670
un ver iz geven oyf di andere shtok?

242
00:11:30,351 --> 00:11:32,404
oyf di, fun di BAKERY dort?

243
00:11:31,532 --> 00:11:33,247
NO, fun, fun hoyz.

244
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:34,513
fun hoyz hobn gevoynt yidn.

245
00:11:35,363 --> 00:11:36,990
ober s'hot gehert tsu aykh.

246
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,888
NO.

247
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:39,142
s'iz geven, ah tsu a- feter.

248
00:11:39,042 --> 00:11:43,643
di BA- vu di BAKERY iz gevezn hot gehert tsu mayn feter Fishl VASERMAN.

249
00:11:39,142 --> 00:11:40,612
tsu ayer feter.

250
00:11:44,509 --> 00:11:48,232
iz vemen's hoyz iz geven dos hoyz vu ir hot gevoynt?

251
00:11:44,762 --> 00:11:46,224
iz geven a yid.

252
00:11:46,922 --> 00:11:49,990
iz dos ⟨vu undz ho'mir⟩ gevoynt iz gevezn

253
00:11:49,990 --> 00:11:54,375
mayn shvegerin's foter. er hot geheysn Mendl FREYDNBERG.

254
00:11:55,073 --> 00:11:56,788
hot balangt tsu mayn

255
00:11:56,895 --> 00:11:59,825
tsu mayn shveger's. mayn bruder hot geheyrat

256
00:12:00,085 --> 00:12:02,728
dem eygntimer's a tokhter. ir farshteyt?

257
00:12:04,810 --> 00:12:07,680
s'iz geven modern dortn? ir hot gehat

258
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:09,360
vaser ineveynik?

259
00:12:08,657 --> 00:12:09,632
NO.

260
00:12:09,632 --> 00:12:12,481
Poyln iz geven zeyer tsurikgeshtanen

261
00:12:13,315 --> 00:12:16,633
un zenen gevezn in dem shtetl

262
00:12:17,010 --> 00:12:18,829
di yidn ho'mir gelebt

263
00:12:18,829 --> 00:12:20,717
zeyer a shver lebn.

264
00:12:21,482 --> 00:12:26,926
di yidn hobn zikh farnumen mit melokhes. s'iz geven shusters, shnayders, stolyers

265
00:12:27,085 --> 00:12:30,825
afile KOWALs. veyst a kovel, m'hot ge- ferd ongetun di

266
00:12:31,185 --> 00:12:38,013
un a teyl yidn ho'mir ge- geven kleyn hendler. gehat kleyne STOREkes vos m'hot koym gemakht a lebn.

267
00:12:38,492 --> 00:12:39,937
akhuts dem

268
00:12:40,382 --> 00:12:43,093
zenen yidn gevorn diskriminirt.

269
00:12:44,348 --> 00:12:49,387
s'iz geven zekhtsik protsent fun di bafelkerung in dem shtot iz geven yidn

270
00:12:49,798 --> 00:12:54,348
ober keyn eyn yid hot nisht gearbet nisht far di shtot regirung

271
00:12:54,473 --> 00:12:56,002
un nisht far di

272
00:12:56,076 --> 00:13:00,983
g- regirung UNK vos iz geven tsum bayshpil di shtayer amt. dos hot geheysn oyf poylish

273
00:13:00,983 --> 00:13:02,685
URZAD SKARBOWY

274
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,811
vi yidn hobn getsolt shtayern.

275
00:13:05,172 --> 00:13:10,222
hobn dort gearbet a sakh mentshn, ober keyn eyn yid hot nisht sh- a yid iz nisht geven basheftikt.

276
00:13:10,222 --> 00:13:12,082
m'hot diskriminirt

277
00:13:12,082 --> 00:13:14,329
un derfar hobn yidn zikh gemuzt farnemen

278
00:13:14,419 --> 00:13:18,969
mit vos m'hot nor gekent. m'iz geg- m'iz geganen in dorf arayn, gekoyft dortn

279
00:13:19,245 --> 00:13:22,026
⟨ober⟩ a hun, a bisl eyer tsu farkoyfn

280
00:13:22,026 --> 00:13:24,875
es iz geven an orem un shver lebn.

281
00:13:25,033 --> 00:13:28,025
iz, me ken zogn az s'iz geven a kleyne teyl

282
00:13:28,025 --> 00:13:30,017
fun di yidishe bafelkerung

283
00:13:30,017 --> 00:13:31,687
vos zey hobn gehat parnose.

284
00:13:31,687 --> 00:13:35,077
keyn milyonern iz nisht gevezn. s'iz geven a por raykhe yidn

285
00:13:35,479 --> 00:13:36,553
iz gevezn.

286
00:13:37,622 --> 00:13:38,544
o-

287
00:13:37,656 --> 00:13:40,029
un vos, fun vos zaynen zey geven raykh?

288
00:13:40,086 --> 00:13:43,387
di yidn UNK gehandlt mit di velder.

289
00:13:44,052 --> 00:13:46,898
es iz geven eyner a yid, hot er geheysn

290
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:50,812
UNK

291
00:13:51,088 --> 00:13:52,584
Mordkhe Lenger.

292
00:13:52,810 --> 00:13:54,975
er hot gehandlt mit pritsim

293
00:13:54,975 --> 00:13:59,233
mit velder. er iz geven a raykher, raykher yid. s'iz geven nokh a por yidn azelkhe.

294
00:13:59,273 --> 00:14:00,549
raykhe yidn.

295
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:09,121
UNK un di resht hobn a teyl vos iz geven a por protsent, dos hobn mir gehat gevelblekh, zey hobn gehat parnose, nisht raykh geven.

296
00:14:09,499 --> 00:14:14,235
ober di yugnt, far di yugnt iz gevezn, zey hobn nisht gehat keyn tsukunft.

297
00:14:15,675 --> 00:14:17,694
s'iz nisht geven vos tsu tun.

298
00:14:18,207 --> 00:14:22,026
⟨es⟩ zenen gev- s'iz geven kamashn makhers, shusters, shnayders. m'hot

299
00:14:22,026 --> 00:14:26,379
az di eygntimers vos zey hobn gefirt di b- di, di fabriklekh

300
00:14:26,379 --> 00:14:28,039
hobn aleyn geven oreme layt.

301
00:14:28,095 --> 00:14:30,839
vos hot shoyn gekent an arbeter bay zey derlebn?

302
00:14:32,078 --> 00:14:34,707
es iz geven zeyer, zeyer a shver lebn

303
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:39,750
un dertsu nokh vos UNK s'hot zikh farshtarkt, der Poy- in Poyln der antisemitizm

304
00:14:39,975 --> 00:14:41,825
iz geven zeyer shtark.

305
00:14:41,950 --> 00:14:45,673
a gantse geven poylishe mentshn, oykhet oreme

306
00:14:46,455 --> 00:14:47,461
ober

307
00:14:47,653 --> 00:14:49,368
zenen gevezn

308
00:14:49,864 --> 00:14:52,999
der p- hot nisht gelitn fun di diskriminatsye.

309
00:14:52,999 --> 00:14:54,988
UNK ⟨vayl⟩ s'iz nisht geven keyn yid

310
00:14:55,247 --> 00:15:00,286
a yid hot gehat DOUBLE. i er iz g- hot nisht gehat keyn parnose, un i er hot gelitn vayl er iz a yid

311
00:15:01,457 --> 00:15:06,750
un s'iz geshtanen far di milkhome, oyf d- hob ikh a mol ge- hob ikh geleyent ergets

312
00:15:07,212 --> 00:15:11,357
az in zibn un draysik oder in akht un draysikstn yor

313
00:15:11,430 --> 00:15:13,904
iz avekgeforn a delegatsye

314
00:15:14,282 --> 00:15:18,244
fun antisemitishe advokatn, LAWYERS

315
00:15:18,244 --> 00:15:20,131
keyn Daytshland, keyn Minkhn

316
00:15:20,644 --> 00:15:25,683
oystsugefinen di Niremberger gezetsn vos di daytshn hobn ongenumen in Niremberg

317
00:15:26,078 --> 00:15:27,489
f- far yidn.

318
00:15:27,883 --> 00:15:29,024
un

319
00:15:29,115 --> 00:15:32,669
ikh gloyb az es volt nokh genumen a yor tsvey

320
00:15:32,743 --> 00:15:35,153
volt efsher in Poyln gevorn ayngefirt

321
00:15:35,153 --> 00:15:40,331
di Nirembirger gezetsn v- vegn yidn, vegn diskriminirn yidn

322
00:15:41,215 --> 00:15:43,369
az der poylisher premyer

323
00:15:43,645 --> 00:15:45,849
er hot geheysn SKLADKOWSKI

324
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:49,680
ven zey hobn ongefaln oyf yidn, m'hot geshlogn

325
00:15:50,395 --> 00:15:54,374
m'hot gemakht pogrom, hot er gezogt me darf nisht shlogn nor boykotirn

326
00:15:54,374 --> 00:15:57,307
UNK, dos heyst meg men boykotirn

327
00:15:57,364 --> 00:15:58,573
nisht koyfn

328
00:15:58,613 --> 00:16:04,564
un az s'iz oysgekumen donershtik vi ikh hob gezogt frier, UNK bay ⟨di⟩ mark tog ⟨ven⟩ es zenen gekumen di poyerim

329
00:16:05,363 --> 00:16:09,339
hobn zikh avekgeshtelt antisemitn studentn bay di gevelber

330
00:16:09,565 --> 00:16:11,061
un geshrign

331
00:16:11,202 --> 00:16:16,092
m- m'hot nisht gelozt arayngeyn di polyakn, "SWOJ DO SWEGO PO SWOJA," dos heyst

332
00:16:16,092 --> 00:16:19,532
polyakn zoln geyn koyfn bay polyakn un nisht bay keyn yidn.

333
00:16:19,723 --> 00:16:21,972
