339
00:16:32,008 --> 00:16:37,233
ir gedenkt azelkhe pasirungen in di frierdike yorn in ts- in di yorn tsvantsik?

340
00:16:35,333 --> 00:16:38,466
yo, dos iz gevezn far di milkhome.

341
00:16:38,016 --> 00:16:41,435
ikh meyn ober in di yorn tsvantsik, nisht in akht un draysik.

342
00:16:40,277 --> 00:16:45,553
di ⟨tsvontsikn⟩ bin ikh, bin ikh alt UNK zibn yor in di tsvontsik, ken ikh nisht gedenken.

343
00:16:46,622 --> 00:16:48,995
un in onheyb fun di draysiker yorn?

344
00:16:48,647 --> 00:16:53,504
in onheyb fun di draysiker yorn iz shoyn geven der antisemitizm farshtarkt azoy

345
00:16:53,504 --> 00:16:56,943
az zenen forgekumen pogromen, zenen forgekumen pogromen

346
00:16:57,068 --> 00:16:59,087
in Tshenstekhev, a shtot

347
00:16:59,667 --> 00:17:00,943
un

348
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:04,672
un nokh in a shtot vu me z- makht pogrom oyf yidn.

349
00:17:05,083 --> 00:17:08,620
un di adv- di universitetn in Poyln

350
00:17:08,948 --> 00:17:10,798
zenen geven a nest

351
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:13,987
fun antisemitizm. di studentn

352
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:16,349
zenen geven di greste antisemitn

353
00:17:17,165 --> 00:17:18,495
un m'hot di yidn

354
00:17:18,495 --> 00:17:22,846
di yidishe studentn hot men getsvungen zoln zitsn oyf di linke zayt.

355
00:17:24,102 --> 00:17:28,247
iz d- d- d- der grester antisemitizm iz geven oyf di universitetn.

356
00:17:28,388 --> 00:17:30,178
un, un in Varshe

357
00:17:30,178 --> 00:17:34,258
iz gevezn yidn vos zey hobn gehandlt mit STRAGANes. ir veyst vos meynt

358
00:17:34,581 --> 00:17:38,425
s- ⟨er zol⟩ gerosh- aroysgeshtelt tishn. m'hot farkoyft frukhtn

359
00:17:38,425 --> 00:17:40,231
farkoyft fish, farkoyft

360
00:17:40,231 --> 00:17:42,737
zenen zey ongefaln. m'hot umgevorfn

361
00:17:42,737 --> 00:17:44,137
un tsebrokhn.

362
00:17:44,137 --> 00:17:47,366
yidn hobn geshtelt iz, in Varshe iz gevezn

363
00:17:47,473 --> 00:17:51,133
di transport arbet, di yidn, gezunte, shtarke yidn

364
00:17:51,133 --> 00:17:53,453
un zey hobn mir farteydikt, di yidishe

365
00:17:53,453 --> 00:17:55,989
di, di UNK di sokh- di sokhrim

366
00:17:56,012 --> 00:17:57,609
un m'hot faryogt di

367
00:17:58,172 --> 00:18:02,655
ober s'iz geven, der antisemitizm iz gevezn a shreklekher in Poyln.

368
00:18:03,336 --> 00:18:05,692
azoy az der daytsh

369
00:18:06,272 --> 00:18:08,324
ven er iz arayn keyn Poyln

370
00:18:08,533 --> 00:18:10,315
hot er gehat a gute

371
00:18:10,744 --> 00:18:16,813
a gute m- ort vi azoy durkhtsufirn. m'hot nisht gehat keyn shterung fun di poylishe bafelkerung.

372
00:18:17,157 --> 00:18:20,796
di poylishe bafelkerung, s'iz geven a teyl a, oykhet oreme

373
00:18:20,937 --> 00:18:22,939
ober zey zenen gevezn

374
00:18:23,046 --> 00:18:24,406
az zey hobn shoyn gekukt

375
00:18:24,406 --> 00:18:29,156
az der daytsh vet aroysfirn di yidn, veln zey kenen araynloyfn farnemen di shtubn

376
00:18:29,156 --> 00:18:32,794
un farkhapn dortn a tish, a shenkl, a UNK

377
00:18:33,306 --> 00:18:36,894
un dos iz di, dos iz geven, der yid iz gevezn

378
00:18:36,900 --> 00:18:38,750
