387
00:18:53,269 --> 00:18:54,039
ye.

388
00:18:55,024 --> 00:18:56,553
s'iz gevezn

389
00:18:57,133 --> 00:19:03,438
dos g- ekonomishe lebn iz geven oysergeveyntlekh shver, ober dos gaystike lebn

390
00:19:03,613 --> 00:19:06,897
bay yidn iz gevezn, iz nisht tsu banemen.

391
00:19:06,972 --> 00:19:10,358
s'hot eksistirt in dem shtetl.

392
00:19:11,038 --> 00:19:18,305
a bundishe organizatsye, a tsienistishe organizatsye, a POYLE tsienistishe organizatsye.

393
00:19:18,463 --> 00:19:22,777
mir hobn gehat a biblyotek fun fuftsn toyznt bikher.

394
00:19:23,155 --> 00:19:27,249
es hot eksistirt a mandolin orkester

395
00:19:27,593 --> 00:19:29,606
a bloz orkester

396
00:19:29,606 --> 00:19:32,025
tsvey dramatishe krayzn

397
00:19:32,233 --> 00:19:36,665
un s'zenen forgekumen yedn shabes kimat lektsyes

398
00:19:36,790 --> 00:19:40,347
vegn politishe, ekonomishe

399
00:19:40,347 --> 00:19:43,618
oder literarishe, un dos yi- gaystike lebn

400
00:19:43,675 --> 00:19:45,542
iz geshtanen zeyer hoykh.

401
00:19:45,733 --> 00:19:51,054
hagam vos dray mentshn, dray arbeter, hobn gekoyft eyn tsaytung.

402
00:19:51,054 --> 00:19:53,878
a folks tsaytung hot gekost tsen groshn.

403
00:19:54,492 --> 00:19:57,627
hot men dray gekoyft, UNK geven arbetsloz

404
00:19:57,627 --> 00:19:58,901
zey hobn nisht gegat

405
00:19:58,901 --> 00:19:59,970
keyn gelt

406
00:20:00,178 --> 00:20:02,048
ober zey hobn nokh gevolt leyenen

407
00:20:02,048 --> 00:20:04,039
es iz geven a leyen zal, ober

408
00:20:04,039 --> 00:20:08,593
m'hot gevolt untershtitsn di tsaytung, hobn dray gekoyft eyn tsaytung.

409
00:20:12,565 --> 00:20:14,786
un vifl shuln zaynen dortn geven?

410
00:20:14,910 --> 00:20:16,524
es iz gevezn

411
00:20:16,547 --> 00:20:17,632
a

412
00:20:17,632 --> 00:20:19,511
