417
00:20:31,487 --> 00:20:33,585
ir veyst vos meynt ovnt kursn

418
00:20:34,047 --> 00:20:35,644
dos iz geven yidishe.

419
00:20:35,903 --> 00:20:37,536
ober di yugnt

420
00:20:37,536 --> 00:20:39,339
hot a sakh geleyent.

421
00:20:39,784 --> 00:20:41,738
s'iz geven bar undz a gortn

422
00:20:41,738 --> 00:20:44,520
hot ir gekent shabes arayngeyn zen

423
00:20:44,593 --> 00:20:47,675
zenen gezitsn yinglekh un meydlekh

424
00:20:47,901 --> 00:20:53,008
ver s'hot geleyent a bukh, ver s'hot geleyent a zhurnal, ver a tsaytung.

425
00:20:53,183 --> 00:20:55,455
di yugnt iz geven bavustzinik.

426
00:20:55,748 --> 00:21:01,479
nor eyn zakh, di ekonomishe situatsye, s'iz nisht gevezn keyn shum tsukunft, keyn shum oysveg.

427
00:21:01,637 --> 00:21:03,335
m'hot nisht gezen keyn shum

428
00:21:03,645 --> 00:21:04,989
keyn shum oysveg.

429
