434
00:21:18,208 --> 00:21:19,698
di malerayen

435
00:21:19,698 --> 00:21:23,029
di shul iz geven hot men gezogt fir hundert yor alt

436
00:21:23,389 --> 00:21:25,269
az dem, bay dem sh-

437
00:21:24,402 --> 00:21:25,476
fir hundert?

438
00:21:25,269 --> 00:21:27,369
fir hundert yor alt d- ikh

