vos heyst far zikh?

506
00:24:45,737 --> 00:24:49,528
ikh hob mit a shutef genumen, gekoyft a por mashinen

507
00:24:49,838 --> 00:24:51,756
un di shusters

508
00:24:53,803 --> 00:24:55,585
di shusters hobn

509
00:24:55,913 --> 00:24:57,233
gebrengt polyakn

510
00:24:57,233 --> 00:25:00,243
zey hobn ⟨mir⟩ gebrengt tsu mir leder, un ikh hob far zey geneyt

511
00:25:01,414 --> 00:25:03,605
un ikh hob gevoynt bazunder,

512
00:25:03,605 --> 00:25:05,773
un ikh hob gearbet ⟨⟩

513
00:25:05,683 --> 00:25:07,381
in velkhn yor iz dos geven?

514
00:25:05,773 --> 00:25:06,673
far di sh-

515
00:25:07,776 --> 00:25:12,950
dos iz geven nayntsn finef un draysik, zeks un draysik, zibn un draysik, biz di milkhome.

516
00:25:14,661 --> 00:25:19,346
