546
00:26:43,049 --> 00:26:43,991
FAMILY.

547
00:26:43,963 --> 00:26:48,513
zent ir geven ne- neenter mit eyn bruder oder shvester vi mit di andere?

548
00:26:48,537 --> 00:26:50,758
neyn. ikh ⟨volt⟩ nisht gezogt dos.

549
00:26:51,237 --> 00:26:53,520
