551
00:26:56,637 --> 00:26:58,487
flegt ir praven shabes?

552
00:26:58,965 --> 00:26:59,836
bite?

553
00:26:59,505 --> 00:27:01,557
flegt ir praven shabes?

554
00:27:01,092 --> 00:27:03,904
yo, bay mi- undz in shtub, der foter

555
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:08,445
iz geven, hagam di brider zenen nisht gevezn azoy religyez

556
00:27:08,445 --> 00:27:10,116
nor fraytik bay di nakht

557
00:27:10,116 --> 00:27:11,970
tsi di shabes

558
00:27:12,010 --> 00:27:13,854
