562
00:27:22,928 --> 00:27:29,098
di mame, di mame flegt fraytik ⟨du⟩ veyst azoy vi in di heym UNK m'hot ales tsugegreyt

563
00:27:29,290 --> 00:27:32,591
m'hot gezen ales tsu tun az d- der shabes

564
00:27:32,783 --> 00:27:34,616
