577
00:28:04,913 --> 00:28:06,324
in shtot arayn

578
00:28:06,769 --> 00:28:08,906
iz er gekumen in shul un

579
00:28:09,081 --> 00:28:10,931
yidn hobn aheymgenumen im

580
00:28:11,511 --> 00:28:12,838
oyf

581
00:28:12,979 --> 00:28:16,415
oyf shabes, hot er gegesn fraytik tsu nakht ⟨di⟩ shabes.

582
00:28:16,928 --> 00:28:20,398
vos zaynen geven di balibtste maykholim vos di mame fleg kokhn?

583
00:28:20,421 --> 00:28:26,861
v- vos iz geven maykholim i- fleg ikh gedenk az se fleg yedn s- kimat yedn sh- fraytik tsu nakhts

584
00:28:27,087 --> 00:28:28,650
