585
00:28:29,415 --> 00:28:31,200
pletslekh mit yoykh

586
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:35,281
mit di pletslekh, ⟨veys⟩ nisht ⟨vos⟩ ir veyst, pletslekh, dos hot men gebakn azolkhe dine

587
00:28:35,727 --> 00:28:38,910
un a shtikl fleysh un a bisl kompot.

588
00:28:40,620 --> 00:28:43,671
tsi flegn yidn brengen tsholnt arayn in bekeray?

589
