591
00:28:48,197 --> 00:28:49,338
tsholnt

592
00:28:49,362 --> 00:28:52,106
un m'hot dos aroysgenumen shabes in di fri

593
00:28:53,378 --> 00:28:56,696
es iz, s'iz a bisl gevezn az

594
00:28:57,310 --> 00:29:01,404
a bisl, vi me zogt epes gelekhter. s'iz geven oreme mentshn

595
00:29:01,613 --> 00:29:05,117
un az zey hobn gezen a raykher yid brengt arayn a tsholnt

596
00:29:05,899 --> 00:29:12,310
iz tsu morgns zenen zey gekumen, hot men ⟨bakumen⟩ nisht ⟨nor⟩ zayn tsholnt, hot er genumen mi- yenems tsholnt.

